      • tileCache

        protected LruMemoryCache<java.lang.String,Tile[]> tileCache
        Memory cache for this tessellator's subdivision tiles. Each entry contains an array of four terrain tiles corresponding to the subdivision of the group's common parent tile. The cache is configured to hold 200 groups, a number tuned to store the tiles needed to navigate a small region, given the tessellator's first level tile delta of 90 degrees, tile dimensions of 32x32 and detail control of 80.
